--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-10-03)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-24)
B: Correct template file name

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-10)
E: Improve Jinja2 filters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
